ED_Title: The situation in the occupied territories of Azerbaijan
ED_DecisionText: At its 107th plenary meeting, on 16 September 2019, the General Assembly decided to defer consideration of the item entitled “The situation in the occupied territories of Azerbaijan” and to include it in the draft agenda of its seventy-fourth session.
ED_Disclaimer: The final version of decisions adopted during the resumed part of the session will be contained in the official record of the GA (A/73/49 (Vol. III) after editorial review.
